Code 

class Solution {
    public int scoreOfString(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int sum = 0;

        for(int i=0; i<n-1; i++) {
            if(i != n-1) {
                sum += Math.abs(s.charAt(i) - s.charAt(i+1));
            } else {
                sum += Math.abs(s.charAt(i) - s.charAt(0));
            }
        }

        return sum;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(n)
Space Complexity : O(1)
